function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.5') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.5!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png') && (sha1_file('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png') != '827cef90ad07d6387183327dade2ea83bf949a5a')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png');
	$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png');
} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png') != '827cef90ad07d6387183327dade2ea83bf949a5a') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/img/ref-r74n.png');
}

}
if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != 'c1482d71ab274246e73b34fbfce4e8f67af02f3f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'c1482d71ab274246e73b34fbfce4e8f67af02f3f') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '6dc38f5f7db44393e08d594393615f6e978d51c4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'c1482d71ab274246e73b34fbfce4e8f67af02f3f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: doc/website/download.html

if (!is_file('doc/website/download.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/download.html');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/download.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/download.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') != '7b0d34e78f616ce1e9e4f0cfa8f22509fd5df3d8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/download.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/download.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/download.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '7b0d34e78f616ce1e9e4f0cfa8f22509fd5df3d8') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '56543575bfee6d37ff2539b7015a6ffc767807ec') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/download.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/download.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/download.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/download.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '7b0d34e78f616ce1e9e4f0cfa8f22509fd5df3d8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/download.html');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: doc/website/examples.html
function writefile_4() {

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZSBlbmQgb2YgdGhlIGRvY3VtZW50IHNvIHRoZSBwYWdlcyBsb2FkIGZhc3RlciAtLT4KICAgIDxzY3JpcHQgc3JjPSJodHRwczovL2NvZGUuanF1ZXJ5LmNvbS9qcXVlcnktMy4yLjEuc2xpbS5taW4uanMiIGludGVncml0eT0ic2hhMzg0LUtKM28yREt0SWt2WUlL'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('M1VFTnptTTdLQ2tSci9yRTkvUXBnNmFBWkdKd0ZETVZOQS9HcEdGRjkzaFhwRzVLa04iIGNyb3Nzb3JpZ2luPSJhbm9ueW1vdXMiPjwvc2NyaXB0PgogICAgPCEtLTxzY3JpcHQ+d2luZG93LmpRdWVyeSB8fCBkb2N1bWVudC53cml0ZSgnPHNjcmlwdCBzcmM9ImJv'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('b3RzdHJhcC9hc3NldHMvanMvdmVuZG9yL2pxdWVyeS1zbGltLm1pbi5qcyI+PFwvc2NyaXB0PicpPC9zY3JpcHQ+CiAgICA8c2NyaXB0IHNyYz0iYm9vdHN0cmFwL2Fzc2V0cy9qcy92ZW5kb3IvcG9wcGVyLm1pbi5qcyI+PC9zY3JpcHQ+LS0+CiAgICA8c2NyaXB0'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IHNyYz0iYm9vdHN0cmFwL2pzL2Jvb3RzdHJhcC5taW4uanMiPjwvc2NyaXB0PgogICAgPCEtLTxzY3JpcHQgc3JjPSJib290c3RyYXAvYXNzZXRzL2pzL3ZlbmRvci9ob2xkZXIubWluLmpzIj48L3NjcmlwdD4tLT4KICA8L2JvZHk+CjwvaHRtbD4K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('doc/website/examples.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/examples.html');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/examples.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/examples.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') != '0002393bc7e381fd9092f1bea91751e59d9110b9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/examples.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/examples.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/examples.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '0002393bc7e381fd9092f1bea91751e59d9110b9') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '58d6d22bfc17737a0d5873e61ab45b79851d895c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/examples.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/examples.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/examples.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/examples.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '0002393bc7e381fd9092f1bea91751e59d9110b9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/examples.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/features.html');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/features.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') != '2dde9d7e9fab7dc16c7be3146172d3326f78a3a5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/features.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/features.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '2dde9d7e9fab7dc16c7be3146172d3326f78a3a5') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '59acba905a38da4560af2c0f355dedaad366dddf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/features.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/features.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/features.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/features.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/features.html') !== '2dde9d7e9fab7dc16c7be3146172d3326f78a3a5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/features.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/support.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/support.html');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/support.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/support.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') != '5b1dcc21b08c3e93637a4d6c946fe319300105b5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/support.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/support.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/support.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== '5b1dcc21b08c3e93637a4d6c946fe319300105b5') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== 'fdf8aca692b410951c938f01b931c1b40189268e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/support.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/support.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/support.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/support.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== '5b1dcc21b08c3e93637a4d6c946fe319300105b5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/support.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '4346f4fe640ae0f0b747ee9b60b7c6a23150f2b7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '4346f4fe640ae0f0b747ee9b60b7c6a23150f2b7') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '9968c5396d21a65f86508ad5f924dc512b012cf7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '4346f4fe640ae0f0b747ee9b60b7c6a23150f2b7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != '467803aeeafe7bce8ab02779acbef74395c19986') {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '467803aeeafe7bce8ab02779acbef74395c19986') {

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
